Linode 为顾客提供多样化的服务<ref name="NJbusiness"/><ref name="pcworld">{{cite web|url = http://www.pcworld.co.nz/article/531754/adobe_patches_critical_vulnerabilities_flash_player_coldfusion/|title = Adobe Patches Critical Vulnerabilities in Flash Player Coldfusion|accessdate = 21 Nov 2013|archive-date = 2017-11-17|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20171117002656/https://www.pcworld.co.nz/article/531754/adobe_patches_critical_vulnerabilities_flash_player_coldfusion/|dead-url = no}}</ref>。它主要提供各种不同价位、不同档次的 VPS 服务器<ref name="pcworld"/>。Linode Manager 和 NodeBalancer允许用户通过一个统一的系统管理多个不同的服务器<ref name="pcworld"/>。2013年9月 Longview 上线。这一服务能够追踪并分析服务器的情况<ref>Bernstein, Peter. </ref><ref name="register">{{cite web|url = http://www.theregister.co.uk/2013/09/06/linode_longview/|title = Linode adds analytics package to Linux cloud|publisher = The Register|author = Jack Clark|date = September 6, 2013|accessdate = September 27, 2013|archive-date = 2020-04-30|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200430041757/https://www.theregister.co.uk/2013/09/06/linode_longview/|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref name="techzone">{{cite web|url = http://www.techzone360.com/topics/techzone/articles/2013/09/05/351999-linode-launches-longview-takes-deep-look-data-center.htm|title = Linode Launches Longview, Takes Deep Look at Data Center and Server Performance|publisher = Tech Zone 360|author = Peter Bernstein|date = September 5, 2013|accessdate = September 27, 2013|archive-date = 2020-04-30|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200430041753/https://www.techzone360.com/topics/techzone/articles/2013/09/05/351999-linode-launches-longview-takes-deep-look-data-center.htm|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref name="whir">{{cite web|url = http://www.thewhir.com/web-hosting-news/linode-launches-longview-for-linux-server-statistics-collection-and-graphing|title = Linode Launches Longview for Linux Server Statistics Collection and Graphing|publisher = The Whir|author = Nicole Henderson|date = September 5, 2013|accessdate = September 27, 2013|archive-date = 2017-11-17|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20171117001510/http://www.thewhir.com/web-hosting-news/linode-launches-longview-for-linux-server-statistics-collection-and-graphing|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref name="bestwebhosting">{{cite web|url = http://bestwebhosting2go.com/linode-releases-longview-new-linux-server-statistics-collection-and-graphing-service-3401/|title = Linode Releases Longview, New Linux Server Statistics Collection And Graphing Service|publisher = Best Web Hosting 2Go|author = John Maxwell|date = September 6, 2013|accessdate = September 27, 2013|deadurl = yes|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130922034754/http://bestwebhosting2go.com/linode-releases-longview-new-linux-server-statistics-collection-and-graphing-service-3401/|archivedate = 2013年9月22日}}</ref>。

