== 安全事故 ==
8名持有[[比特币|比特币]]的 Linode 用户在2012年3月时自己持有的、估计约共40000枚比特币被窃。这些比特币在当时大约相当于7万美元<ref name="FORB">{{cite web|last = Matonis|first = Jon|title = Watch Bitcoin Robbery in Slow Motion|url = http://www.forbes.com/sites/jonmatonis/2012/04/02/watch-bitcoin-robbery-in-slow-motion/|work = Forbes|accessdate = 18 July 2013|archive-date = 2020-11-12|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201112002719/https://www.forbes.com/sites/jonmatonis/2012/04/02/watch-bitcoin-robbery-in-slow-motion/|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref name="TRUK1">{{cite web|last = Leyden|first = John|title = Linode hackers escape with $70K in daring bitcoin heist|url = http://www.theregister.co.uk/2012/03/02/linode_bitcoin_heist/|work = The Register|accessdate = 18 July 2013|archive-date = 2020-05-11|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200511130449/https://www.theregister.co.uk/2012/03/02/linode_bitcoin_heist/|dead-url = no}}</ref>。

2013年，一个叫做 Hack The Planet 的黑客组织利用了 [[Adobe|Adobe]] [[Adobe_ColdFusion|ColdFusion]] 的一个[[漏洞|漏洞]]进入了 Linode 的服务器。Linode 解释道该组织尽管进入服务器但仍不能解密任何与付款有关的个人敏感信息，之后 Linode 重置了所有账户的密码。<ref name="Zdnet">{{cite web|last = Lee|first = Michael|title = VPS host Linode issues customer-wide password reset|url = http://www.zdnet.com/vps-host-linode-issues-customer-wide-password-reset-7000014057/|work = ZDNet|accessdate = 18 July 2013|archive-date = 2014-02-22|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140222123055/http://www.zdnet.com/vps-host-linode-issues-customer-wide-password-reset-7000014057/|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref name="TEC">{{cite web|last = Dumon|first = Marv|title = Amazon Launches Cloud Computing Certification Program - Page 2|url = http://technorati.com/technology/cloud-computing/article/amazon-launches-cloud-computing-certification-program/page-2/|work = Technorati|accessdate = 18 July 2013|deadurl = yes|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131203050142/http://technorati.com/technology/cloud-computing/article/amazon-launches-cloud-computing-certification-program/page-2/|archivedate = 2013年12月3日}}</ref><ref name="TRUK">{{cite web|last = Leyden|first = John|title = Web host Linode, hackers clash over credit-card raid claim|url = http://www.theregister.co.uk/2013/04/16/linode_breach/|work = The Register|accessdate = 18 July 2013|archive-date = 2020-04-30|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200430043940/https://www.theregister.co.uk/2013/04/16/linode_breach/|dead-url = no}}</ref> 同年5月，Linode 为自己的账户引入两步认证功能。<ref name="YH!">{{cite web|last = Bandoim|first = Lana|title = Two-Step Authentication Grows in Popularity|url = http://voices.yahoo.com/two-step-authentication-grows-popularity-12132405.html?cat=15|work = Yahoo! Voices|accessdate = 18 July 2013|deadurl = yes|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130609064506/http://voices.yahoo.com/two-step-authentication-grows-popularity-12132405.html?cat=15|archivedate = 2013年6月9日}}</ref>

2016年1月5日，Linode 在发现有用户登錄凭据泄露后，以安全原因重置了所有用户的密码。<ref>{{cite web|title=Security Notification and Linode Manager Password Reset|url=http://status.linode.com/incidents/ghdlhfnfngnh|publisher=Linode|accessdate=January 5, 2016|archive-date=2020-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201107224001/https://status.linode.com/incidents/ghdlhfnfngnh|dead-url=no}}</ref>

自2015年圣诞节开始，Linode 正受到大规模、频繁的[[DDoS|DDoS]]攻击，根据 Linode 的说法，估计攻击次数达到30轮。 Linode 称，这些攻击是由恶意者通过购买大量[[僵尸网络|僵尸网络]]容量发起，以试图使 Linode 的服务严重受损。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Forster|first1=Alex|title=An update from Linode about the recent DDoS attacks|url=http://status.linode.com/incidents/mmdbljlglnfd|publisher=Linode|accessdate=January 1, 2016|archive-date=2020-11-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201127202220/https://status.linode.com/incidents/mmdbljlglnfd|dead-url=no}}</ref>

